Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.03,0:01:38.24,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}反省ばかりで変われなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.36,0:01:41.53,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}心殺しやり過ごす
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.53,0:01:45.25,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}終わらない懺悔と憂鬱の夜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.04,0:01:54.51,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}完全な自分がどこにもいない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.30,0:02:00.76,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}最低な自分しか見つからない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:42.85,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}成为不了完全的圣人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.60,0:00:49.02,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}无论失败几次都改变不了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.36,0:00:53.65,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}无药可救了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.65,0:00:55.53,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}因为就是做不到嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.53,0:00:58.74,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}说着不该是这样的 逃避现实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.74,0:01:01.95,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}又想要一了百了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.95,0:01:05.08,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}讨厌这样的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:06.79,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}封闭自己自欺欺人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.79,0:01:08.21,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}受伤 哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.21,0:01:11.55,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}即便抱着迷路羔羊的感情入睡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:14.63,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}后悔也完全完全完全无法释怀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.63,0:01:18.30,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}独自不断的钻着牛角尖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.30,0:01:22.26,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}成为不了完全的圣人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.26,0:01:25.35,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}理想总是事与愿违
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:28.69,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}只准备好自责的姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.69,0:01:31.94,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}寻求着那廉价的借口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.94,0:01:34.94,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}无论失败几次都改变不了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.03,0:01:38.24,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}虚心接受屡教不改
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.36,0:01:41.53,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}昧着良心得过且过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.53,0:01:45.25,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}没有尽头的忏悔与忧郁的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.04,0:01:54.51,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}没有完美的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.30,0:02:00.76,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}只有最差劲的自己
Comment: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:06.56,EDJP,,0,0,0,,========================ED==================================
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:08.14,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}始まりはただの恋心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:11.27,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}気づけば唯一無二の拠り所
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:14.11,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}同じ時刻み　齢をとろうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:17.23,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}これからは　お願いさ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:19.07,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}stay with me stay with me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:22.74,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}so long time 隣りにいて　永久に
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:26.08,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}闘いの日々に疲れても
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:28.54,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}怒りの雨に降られても
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:31.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}濡れてしまうならば迷わず
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:33.79,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}俺が代わりにあなたの傘となる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:36.50,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}寒くないよ　隣にいる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:39.01,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}ただそれだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:41.97,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}君は僕の拠り所さ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:45.80,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}その笑顔にまた癒やされる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:48.27,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}世界中　探しても
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:50.43,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}代わりなんていない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:53.40,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}君は僕の拠り所さ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:57.23,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}そこにいるだけでまた満たされる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:11:59.69,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}どんなに傷ついても
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.69,0:12:03.28,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(15,180)\blur2}この身捧げ守るから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:08.14,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}最初不过是单纯的小小恋心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.14,0:11:11.27,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}不觉间却成了我唯一的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:14.11,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}让我们在岁月中一同刻下年华
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:17.23,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}今后也拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.23,0:11:19.07,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}stay with me stay with me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.07,0:11:22.74,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}so long time 永远在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:26.08,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}不论是历战的疲惫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:28.54,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}还是暴风雨的侵袭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:31.00,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}当你脆弱的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:33.79,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}我将毫不犹豫地为你遮风挡雨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:36.50,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}只要你在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:39.01,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}就不会感到寒冷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:41.97,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}你就是我的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:45.80,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}总能被你的微笑治愈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:48.27,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}就算寻遍整个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:50.43,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}也没有谁能代替你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:53.40,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}你就是我的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:57.23,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}在你身边就是我最大的满足
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:11:59.69,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}不管受怎样的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.69,0:12:03.28,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(625,180)\blur2}我都将舍身相护
